{
  "stem": "17301.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was like almost like an multi-grain piece a very thin piece of bread, and a very thin salami, one slice of salami that was like paper thin.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And that was our dinner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And from after that, they locked us into our-- back into the barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We had to go back in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They locked us in there until next morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And this went on for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And one day-- and every morning when we-- when we lined up for zahlappell, I knew that somebody is going to be missing the next day, and which was-- that's exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I try to-- every time my-- my-- Mengele came around, and if my mother was pale, I would go in the back and I would pinch her a little bit.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And it brought a little color into her face.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Because it hurt her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "So I hurt her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And it brought a little color into her face, just to make sure that they're not gonna take her away from me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Because she was very, very pale.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And I did it every single day, day after day, to make sure that she was still with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "But I saw a lot of people being taken out of the lines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I never saw them again, until I found out later on what was happening to them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And one day, it-- we were there maybe two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And one day they came and they selected a few people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "We didn't know for what, and I thought to myself, they're going to select us for-- for work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "I'm going to volunteer again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And naturally, my mother-- it didn't go well over with my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "She didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But I did anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
